Promise.

1720
01:09:50,124 --> 01:09:53,210
[ambulance horn honking]

1721
01:09:53,211 --> 01:09:54,503
[sighs]

1722
01:09:54,504 --> 01:09:56,046
County ER, Medic 42.

1723
01:09:56,047 --> 01:09:58,465
[dispatch] <i>Medic 42,
this is County. Go ahead.</i>

1724
01:09:58,466 --> 01:10:01,760
County, Medic 42
