Fuck your documentation!

1844
01:15:18,453 --> 01:15:20,204
Fuck the fakers.

1845
01:15:20,205 --> 01:15:22,206
Fuck the bullshit calls.

1846
01:15:22,207 --> 01:15:23,957
Fuck every shoplifter
