the lookie-loos.

1856
01:15:48,149 --> 01:15:49,234
Fuck the dead ones.

1857
01:15:49,693 --> 01:15:50,776
Fuck the live ones.

1858
01:15:50,777 --> 01:15:52,528
Fuck this bullshit pay.

1859
01:15:52,529 --> 01:15:54,655
Fuck me! Fuck you!

1860
01:15:54,656 --> 01:15:56,615
Fuck this job!

1861
01:15:56,616 --> 01:15:58,075
